ny piece is installed.<\/li><li>Bespoke Selection<br\/>We curate and customise pieces from our handcrafted collections — including marble furniture, statement mirrors, seating, and more.<\/li><li>Execution & Styling<br\/>Our team manages delivery, installation, and final styling — layering textures, lighting, and accessories for a beautifully finished space.<\/li><\/ol>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_QUjPBn","heading_RAzcxH","richtext_9R6xC9"],"name":"t:sections.image_with_text.presets.image_with_text.name","settings":{"color_scheme":"","separate_section_with_border":false,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CAM02_0f2e4144-deab-4f68-b40c-21fb13962b23.jpg","reveal_on_scroll":false,"image_position":"start","content_width":"sm","remove_vertical_spacing":true}},"image_with_text_9zGfAe":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_4cndCw":{"type":"subheading","disabled":true,"settings":{"text":"Subheading"}},"heading_74DPTm":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"Why Choose Us","heading_tag":"h1"}},"richtext_qwjKdY":{"type":"richtext","settings":{"content":"<ul><li>Handcrafted in Dubai<br\/>All furniture is locally made with high-quality materials and attention to detail.<\/li><li>Tailored to You<br\/>Every project is fully customized — from finishes and fabrics to spatial flow.<\/li><li>Turnkey Experience<br\/>From concept to completion, we manage the entire process so you don’t have to.<\/li><li>Signature Aesthetic<br\/>Clean, calm, neutral luxury — thoughtfully curated to elevate your everyday.<\/li><\/ul><p><br\/><\/p><h4>Start Your Project<\/h4><p>We work with clients across Dubai and the region on private homes, investment properties, and commercial spaces.<\/p><p>Let’s bring your vision to life.<br\/>Book a consultation or reach out to us below.<br\/><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_4cndCw","heading_74DPTm","richtext_qwjKdY"],"name":"t:sections.image_with_text.presets.image_with_text.name","settings":{"color_scheme":"","separate_section_with_border":false,"ima